Nona Gaprindashvili vs Maia Chiburdanidze
European Women's Rapid Championship, Monte Carlo (2019), Round 6
Queen's gambit declined (D30)

The European Women's Rapid Championship is an 11-round Swiss tournament taking place from 30 November to 1 December 2019 in Monaco.

Players receive 15 minutes for the entire game, plus a 10-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.europechess.org
